author: Sheena McGinley
title: Watch: Bradley talks fake babies, Clint Eastwood's squirrel obsession and gets handsy on Ellen
text:
As Clint Eastwood impressions go, this here impersonation by a bending Bradley Cooper, complete with nuts and squirrels is something to behold.
As for him getting handsy with Ellen, well they enjoyed a spot of cookery with the host - because that's what a daytime TV show without a spot of cookery. From the juggling carrots to the nuanced hand gestures (which he'd know all about given his prowess with the fake baby while filming American Sniper) - is there NO end to this man's talent?!
